    "output": "```python\ndef fibonacci(n):\n    \"\"\"计算斐波那契数列的第 n 项\"\"\"\n    if n <= 0:\n        return 0\n    elif n == 1:\n        return 1\n    \n    a, b = 0, 1\n    for _ in range(2, n + 1):\n        a, b = b, a + b\n    return b\n```",
